rgiveness is at a time of power.\u201d Source: al-Taw\u0101\u1e0du\u2019 wal-Khum\u016bl 151 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0633\u064f\u0648\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u0632\u0650 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0642\u0627\u0644\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33042,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/02\/abu-hatim-without-vengeance\/","url_meta":{"origin":18326,"position":3},"title":"Abu Hatim on Hilm: Graceful patience to forgive without vengeance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Hibban reported: Abu Hatim, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cForbearance is most graceful when it is given despite having the power to take revenge.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-\u2018Uqala\u0304 99 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u062d\u0628\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648 \u062d\u0627\u062a\u0645 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u062d\u0644\u0645 \u0623\u062c\u0645\u0644 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u0643\u0648\u0646 \u0645\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0642\u062a\u062f\u0631 \u0639\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0646\u062a\u0642\u0627\u0645 99\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33816,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/25\/fudayl-always-recommend-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":18326,"position":4},"title":"Fudayl on Forgiveness: Always recommend mercy and forbearance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"'Abdu Samad reported: Al-Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf a man comes to you complaining about another man, then say: O brother, forgive him, as forgiveness is closer to righteousness. If he says my heart cannot tolerate forgiveness, but rather retaliation as Allah Almighty has\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33665,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/artah-revenge-believers-egos\/","url_meta":{"origin":18326,"position":5},"title":"Artah on Revenge: Believers do not take revenge for their egos","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Khallal reported: Artah ibn al-Mundhir, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe believer does not seek vengeance for the sake of himself. The Quran and Sunnah have prevented him from that. He has been restrained.\u201d Source: al-Amr bil-Ma\u02bbru\u0304f lil-Khalla\u0304l 1\/29 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u062e\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0644 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0646\u0652\u0630\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0642\u0